# meetings/ holds runtime recordings of real meetings. Keep them out
# of GitHub's language stats (`linguist-vendored`), out of diff renderers
# (`-diff` so a diff doesn't surface real transcript bytes), and out
# of merge auto-resolution. Test fixtures live under
# tests/fixtures/journals/ and are derived via scripts/scrub_journal.py.
meetings/** linguist-vendored
meetings/** -diff
meetings/** -merge
